title: Sunday Catch Up
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: I can't wait for the trailer breakdown video! Love you Mary, you're such a positive beacon of hope in the AHS community. Keep being you, you inspire me. :)

I have a theory that the outposts are previous locations from the previous seasons.

Also, i think all the witches from the picture appear in the same time.

Hey Mary 

I have been watching your videos for a really long time. I just love how passionate you are about the show and you're a massive geek like me :) I'm from the Republic of Ireland and we speak Gaeilge, or native Irish. I'm pretty sure Scáthach isn't pronounced like Skath-itch. Scáthach in Irish would be pronounced like Skaw-huk. I think so anyways, don't mean to come off like the grammar police lol! It sounds more authentic to the character as well as it sounds more rough and primal, like Scáthach herself! :)
I’m dead, you gave your son the countdown😂😂
